WEBVTT

00:02:28.333 --> 00:02:31.643
Science is pushing for treatments,

00:02:31.667 --> 00:02:33.250
dreaming of cures,

00:02:34.583 --> 00:02:38.518
but loosening that grip of stigma and fear

00:02:38.542 --> 00:02:43.059
could ease the pain
of so many people right now.

00:02:43.083 --> 00:02:47.083
And luckily, meaningful connection
doesn't take a pill.

00:02:48.167 --> 00:02:50.101
It takes reaching out.

00:02:50.125 --> 00:02:52.458
It takes listening.

00:02:53.125 --> 00:02:54.958
And it takes a dose of wonder.

00:02:56.083 --> 00:02:59.518
That really has become my unending quest,

00:02:59.542 --> 00:03:01.559
set in motion by Alice